                Última sinc: {new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}
              </div>
            </div>

            {renderContent()}

          </div>
        </main>

        {/* Overlay for mobile menu */}
        {mobileMenuOpen && (
          <div 
            className="fixed inset-0 bg-black/50 z-20 md:hidden"
            onClick={() => setMobileMenuOpen(false)}
          ></div>
        )}
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};

export default App;

To implement the missing modules (`incidentes`, `exploits`, `zerodays`, `cves`, `alertas`, `fuentes`, `mitigaciones`), I will create a generic **`ResourceManager`** component. This component will dynamically build the table list and the create/edit form based on a configuration object, avoiding code duplication for these 7 similar modules.

Here are the updated and new files:

1.  **`types.ts`**: Added data models for all new modules.
2.  **`services/api.ts`**: Added generic CRUD logic (`fetchResources`, `saveResource`, `deleteResource`) and updated the Dashboard to count real data.
3.  **`components/ResourceManager.tsx`**: Created the generic component to manage these lists.
4.  **`App.tsx`**: Configured and rendered the `ResourceManager` for each tab.

